com.ostrichemulators.semtool.rdf.engine.util

Class SemtoolStructureManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ostrichemulators.semtool.rdf.engine.util.SemtoolStructureManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StructureManager

    public final class SemtoolStructureManagerImpl
extends Object
implements StructureManager
    An implementation that queries the IEngine for SEMTOOL.Structure triples. This class is *not* thread-safe, but it is very lightweight. Note that no matter what is passed into these functions, top-level results are returned...so, for example, if the Person concept has three possible properties, but an instance of Person is passed into getPropertiesOf, three properties will be returned, even if that particular instance doesn't have any of them set.
    Author:
    ryan
